name: Mija - Most Beautiful Song in the World

metadata.description:
On a rainy day in Brooklyn, NYC circa 2017(??) Mija walked into a strangers tiny and gear-packed studio.  This stranger was Mark Evans.  That day they wrote a song together, unknowing that they would continue to create music for years to come.  

Here is "The Most Beautiful Song in the World"

The final song to be minted off my album "Desert Trash" 

Tune in for the *mint livestream* at Koop.xyz 

This Thurs Nov 17th @ 5pm PST 

Join the collector telegram chat: https://guild.xyz/mija-collectors
